Extract tasks as JSON array: [{"task", "requester", "assignee", "assigned_at", "source_ts", "deadline", "category"}]
- "task": Concise %s summary.
- "category": "todo", "waiting", or "promise".
- "source_ts": ID from [ID:...].
- "deadline": Explicit date/time if available.
- MISSING FIELDS: Use empty string "" for any unknown fields. NEVER use "undefined" or "unknown" as strings.